63180_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YijJVbs9GI8Q7kNvgEmc6QC&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCnH7c3QuuimYUzvNdBuDw3XoS-7Mp5VG4GafvSjxq8-g&oe=670BC131"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Trailer_Preorder_v1_ThumbnailB.png", "id": "2457094281347939", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75286673_2457094284681272_2062835017525816130_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yi2j3-Z2Ra8Q7kNvgGwV57A&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD6KBuPi3rzcdbHz4O-SUfnQx6PZcg625IInB2IPiCZqg&oe=670BC61F"}, "display_name": "Snapstick", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# FEATURES\n- Over 600 puzzles\n- Over 5 hours of real good gameplay\n- Over 60 unique mechanics\n- 0 apologies\n- There are 5 bullet points\n\n\n# THINGS YOU'LL DO\n- Grab\n- Snap\n- Stick\n- Win\n- Buy\n- This\n- Game\n\n\n# EVEN MORE INTERESTING DETAILS\n- Over 600 puzzles designed by a multi-award-winning puzzle designer who is much better at designing puzzles than writing store copy\n- Over 2 jokes written by an award-winning puzzle designer who is much better at designing puzzles than writing over 2 jokes\n- Featuring music by the legendary Grant Kirkhope (Banjo-Kazooie, GoldenEye 007, Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle), who is much better at designing puzzles than writing music, but he had very controlling parents\n- Dogs\n- Passthrough and hands support, because it's hip\n- Music\n- Over 20 unresolved low-priority bugs\n- \u2026And so much more!!!\n- Anticlimactic bullet-points\n\n[headset and controllers sold separately]", "short_description": "Snapstick is a bonkers puzzle game about love. Play delirious, VR-rich mechanics and experience themes of toilet love, dog infidelity, secret-agent-couple's-counseling, ASMR planets, and more. It gets weird."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mydogzorro.com/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "My Dog Zo